Paper: hep-th/9610094

Date: 1996-10-14

Title: Boundary ABF Models

Authors: Tetsuji Miwa and Robert Weston

Comments: 26 pages, Latex, uses amssymbols.sty and pb-diagram.sty, 3 ps figures

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B486 (1997) 517-545

We diagonalise the transfer matrix of boundary ABF models using bosonizedvertex operators. We compute the boundary S-matrix and check the scaling limitagainst known results for perturbed boundary conformal field theories.